WEBVTT

00:00:07.544 --> 00:00:10.872
After witnessing the violent rage
shown by babies

00:00:10.872 --> 00:00:14.943
whenever deprived of an item
they considered their own,

00:00:14.943 --> 00:00:18.624
Jean Piaget, a founding father
of child psychology,

00:00:18.624 --> 00:00:22.465
observed something profound
about human nature.

00:00:22.465 --> 00:00:26.654
Our sense of ownership emerges
incredibly early.

00:00:26.654 --> 00:00:28.903
Why are we so clingy?

00:00:28.903 --> 00:00:31.483
There's a well-established phenomenon
in psychology